data.description: Nestled in a highly sought-after neighborhood, this traditional-style residence boasts five bedrooms, three bathrooms, and a spacious basement, providing ample space for comfortable living. The timeless design of the house is complemented by its charming exterior, featuring classic architectural elements that blend seamlessly with the surrounding community. Inside, the well-appointed bedrooms offer a perfect balance of privacy and shared living spaces, ensuring both personal retreats and areas for family gatherings. The three bathrooms are thoughtfully designed with modern fixtures and finishes, providing convenience and style. A highlight of this property is the fenced-in yard, providing a secure and private outdoor space for recreation and relaxation. With its ideal location, classic design, and functional layout, this home is a perfect fit for those seeking a harmonious blend of traditional charm and modern comfort in a coveted neighborhood.   Seller is offering 5k in seller-paid closing costs with an accepted offer to be used however the buyer would need.
